    <div>An article in a 1649 Tatler references three gentlemen in Bath scooping water from the spar and “toasting” the Health of the Women of Bath.  </div>
    <div>Today, the toastmaster is typically charge with ensuring an event goes to schedule with particular attention to all event organisation and etiquette.</div>
    <div>Such events typically include </div>
